{"tid":1323221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721後 政府再唔回應 我地要真全城開花","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T20:09:16.000Z","uid":258088,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"70928901a51834bbdad54767b607f3c23a1e2c6a","tid":1323221,"uid":258088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"⚠️超大型野餐注意⚠️<br />\n有鑑於近日「集中地區野餐」被極黑城力圍堵清場，導致玩家損失慘重。有見及此，眾人有少少建議：<br />\n👉🏼於十八區同時遍地開花👈🏼原因如下<br />\n1. 分散敵方勢力。<br />\n極黑勢力配備水炮車3架、軍力3萬、好多唔同種彈<br />\n2. 迴響力大<br />\n政府話一個地方示威可以係暴動，成個社會一齊示威可以叫咩？革命<br />\n<br />\n原因係近幾次大型野餐都集中係同一個地方進行，例如金鐘、上水、旺角、沙田，極黑勢力都可以由朝早佈置到夜晚，目的就係想包圍我地，將我地一網打盡。所以如果我地再集中地區，佢地都係繼續集中火力打同一個地方。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地可以係自己嗰區講訴求：<br />\n1. 敵方得3架水炮車，射得去邊？<br />\n2. 軍力三萬幾人，30000人除18區=1666，頂盡2000人<br />\n我地人可以好多，加上熟自己嗰區，流動性高，容易be water。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好去金鐘 而係去金鐘前或後都可以咁做<br />\n<br />\n死守無意思 除非你想長守 好似2014金鐘咁<br />\n<br />\n我知道群龍無首係好可怕，但最可怕嘅係被動，所謂嘅Be Water，係主動、機動性高。<br />\n<br />\n另外請謹記，香港人抗爭，係為7大訴求，不為洩憤。<br />\n- 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n- 永久完全撤回逃犯條例<br />\n- 釋放所有反送中被捕抗爭示威者<br />\n- 追究警察濫權<br />\n- 撤回暴動定性<br />\n- 永不實行社會信用評分系統<br />\n- 收回多功能智慧監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n有咩行動就去做，亦都請大家記住，能抗爭至今，全靠<br />\n不分化、不割𥱊、不篤灰<br />\n點解去到中段，分化越黎越嚴重？<br />\n<br />\n手足請謹記，我地對抗嘅係極權，唔係人民<br />\n抗爭初心係主線，唔係打警察，佢地都係傀儡，打狗只係支線。<br />\n<br />\n若721政府再不回應訴求，往後定必行動再升級，全城開花<br />\nGroup Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Ezp5AVD5YuKcg8WTJOmezA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEzp5AVD5YuKcg8WTJOmezA&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=8a509917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Ezp5AVD5YuKcg8WTJOmezA</a><br />\n廣播台<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEYH6e7_NVh7Pbag4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEYH6e7_NVh7Pbag4A&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=7f6bc9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEYH6e7_NVh7Pbag4A</a><br />\nLIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1174923758/4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1174923758%2F4&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1b72ca79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1174923758/4</a>"},{"pid":"a9f24bfe43d31dcc17e476e4ff8c5feec3e9c984","tid":1323221,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5fb5121a12b5f98360350fbfc69d1a0a82693f49","tid":1323221,"uid":258088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264e965d0dfa7c87f54edd973b901de80ccb1f6b","tid":1323221,"uid":258088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"LIHKG 條link 廢 入group先"},{"pid":"e3106a7c83ec22bc109b0bbdbe0242aef43fc80e","tid":1323221,"uid":258088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74876dc1099b32971bce445403b4cbe2caf19144","tid":1323221,"uid":258088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"推呀 幫手"},{"pid":"9e3fcf31c175452ce2d61fc558803bbae0fbbe99","tid":1323221,"uid":25